OL,3,CCare sector may become 'irreparably
OL,4,Cbroken' without more support, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMore support is needed for the care
OL,8,Fsector in the next Budget or it may
OL,9,Fbecome "irreparably broken", a union
OL,10,Fhas warned.
OL,12,FUnite the Union says NHS Scotland
OL,13,Freportedly spent #440 million on
OL,14,Fhospital beds, with one in nine
OL,15,Foccupied by patients who could not
OL,16,Fleave hospital due to delayed
OL,17,Fdischarge in the 12 months leading up
OL,18,Fto April 2025.
