OL,4,Cbroken' without more support, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FUnite argued this money was squandered
OL,8,Fand could have been given to the
OL,9,Fsocial care sector for patients in
OL,10,Fneed of support.
OL,12,FUnite says 28% of delayed discharges
OL,13,Fare due to awaiting a place at a care
OL,14,Fhome, a further 27% are waiting on
OL,15,Fcare home arrangements being finished,
OL,16,F27% due to complex delays, 14% are in
OL,17,Fneed of a community care assessment
OL,18,Fand the remaining 4% were still in
OL,19,Fhospital due to other reasons.
