OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSharon Graham, Unite general
OL,8,Fsecretary, said: "The Scottish
OL,9,Fgovernment has a clear choice to
OL,10,Fsupport frontline social care before
OL,11,Fthe system becomes irreparably broken.
OL,13,F"It's time for the politicians to back
OL,14,Four social care workers and that only
OL,15,Fcomes through investment in people and
OL,16,Fservices."
