OL,3,CCare sector may become 'irreparably
OL,4,Cbroken' without more support, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIn September, Unite laid out a series
OL,8,Fof demands for the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment, which were to raise the
OL,10,Fpay for social care workers, increase
OL,11,Ffunding for the industry and to engage
OL,12,Fwith stakeholders to set out future
OL,13,Fplans for the sector.
OL,15,FShauna Wright, Unite lead officer for
OL,16,Fsocial care in Scotland, said:
OL,17,F"Scotland's social care workers are
OL,18,Fclosely watching the Scottish
OL,19,Fgovernment as it sets out their
OL,20,Fpriorities for the coming year.
